{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"868162a68e","title":"新四军的任务不是向南发展而是支持现有根据地","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"088e5abac9","index":0,"year":1942,"month":7,"day":6,"articleId":"868162a68e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6b1ae7e03a","type":"paragraph","text":"新四军的任务不是向南发展","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"868162a68e"},{"id":"be20f04001","type":"paragraph","text":"而是支持现有根据地","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"868162a68e"},{"id":"73b0d65b58","type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年7月6日）曾、赖，并告陈、刘：电悉。（一）七七宣言已广播，谅收到。（二）浙江战局不久将告一段落，日寇新的步骤现尚难断定，但你们须准备应付敌之“扫荡”。我们军队的任务不是向南发展，而是支持现有根据地，前已于复陈毅同志电中说明了","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"868162a68e"},{"id":"07a0d0f7d4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"868162a68e"},{"id":"cf08b58aa1","type":"paragraph","text":"鱼[1]曾、赖，指曾山、赖传珠，当时分别任中共中央华中局委员装组织部部长和新四军参谋长。陈、刘，指陈教、刘少奇，当时分别任新四军代军长和政治委员。[2]七七宣言，指1942年7月7日中国共产党为纪念抗战五周年发表的","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"868162a68e"}],"page":{"id":"3a4eac68da","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"868162a68e","start":98,"end":98}}}},"__N_SSG":true}